quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  26,1,Taa Siin Miim
  26,2,Those are the signs of the book that makes clear
  26,3,You will perhaps kill yourself with grief because they do not believe
  26,4,"If We will, We can send down on them a sign from the sky, so that their necks would remain bowed down before it"
  26,5,And there does not come to them any new reminder from the Beneficent (God) but they turn away from it
  26,6,"So they have denied (it), therefore the news of that which they mock at, will come to them"
  26,7,Did they not see towards the earth how many beneficial (things) of every kind have We caused to grow in it
  26,8,There is certainly a sign in that but the majority of them does not believe
  26,9,"And your Lord ! He is certainly the Mighty, the Merciful"